    Derived from avinput2annovardb.py in the original project.
    Core logic for converting ClinVar .avinput files to ANNOVAR database
    format is preserved; the implementation has been refactored for
    streaming I/O, immutability, type hints, and improved error handling.

  - src/annovar_db_sync/clinvar.py
    The NCBI FTP discovery and MD5-based update-check strategy is inspired
